 be additional evidence of two distinct populations\npossibly having two different formation pathways, with companion mass as a\nprimary indicator of most likely formation scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Dec 2022 20:40:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-12"}
