k, we also integrated SDC-Scissor into the context\nof an industrial organization in the automotive domain to demonstrate how it\ncan be used in industrial settings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2022 10:46:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-12"}
